msgid "以下は最低限の使いやすさを備えた `init.vim` の例です："
msgstr "Here is an example of `init.vim` with minimal usability:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:84
msgid "4. エイリアス"
msgstr "4. Alias"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:87
msgid "エイリアスの推奨設定"
msgstr "Recommended settings for aliases"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:97
msgid ""
"`vim` や `view` のエイリアスを設定することで、nvim をより快適に利用できます。 ただし、ここでは、`vi` "
"だけはオリジナルのままにしておきます。純粋に `vi` を使いたいときもあるからです。"
msgstr ""
"You can use nvim more comfortably by setting an alias for `vim` or `view`. "
"However, for now, we will leave `vi` as the original. There are times when "
"you just want to use `vi`."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:102
msgid "5. sudo nvim は 避けるべき"
msgstr "5. sudo nvim should be avoided"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:105
msgid "`sudo nvim` は非推奨"
msgstr "`sudo nvim` is deprecated"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:107
msgid "nvim は以下の場所に一時ファイルやセッションファイルを保存します："
msgstr "nvim stores temporary and session files in the following locations:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:114
msgid ""
"ログインユーザの環境下で初のnevimの起動を `sudo nvim` として実行してしまうと、これらのファイルが root "
"所有になり、以降の通常起動でエラーが発生します。"
msgstr ""
"If you start nevim for the first time as a logged-in user with `sudo nvim`, "
"these files will be owned by root and an error will occur on subsequent "
"normal startups."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:117
msgid "例：発生するエラー"
msgstr "Example: Error that occurs"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:126
msgid "対策： `sudoedit` を使う"
msgstr "Solution: Use `sudoedit`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:128
msgid "安全に root 権限のファイルを編集する方法"
msgstr "How to safely edit files with root privileges"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:135
msgid "この方法では、nvim はユーザー権限のまま一時ファイルを編集し、保存時に root が上書きします。"
msgstr ""
"This way, nvim edits the temporary file with user privileges, and root "
"overwrites it when saving."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-06-nvim-initail-setup.rst:138
msgid "所有権の修復が必要な場合"
msgstr "When ownership needs to be restored"

